<div class="riskr-careers">

  <div class="riskr-careers__hero page-width">
    <p class="riskr-careers__eyebrow">Careers</p>
    <h1 class="riskr-careers__headline">
      Join the team.<br>
      Operationalize your potential.
    </h1>
    <p class="riskr-careers__subhead">
      We are always looking for exceptional individuals who are passionate about disrupting the intersection of apparel and corporate linguistics.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="riskr-careers__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-careers__culture page-width">
    <div class="riskr-careers__label-col">
      <span class="riskr-careers__label">Our Culture</span>
    </div>
    <div class="riskr-careers__content-col">
      <p>At Riskr, we move fast, break things (mostly paradigms), and hold each other accountable to a shared set of values that we haven't fully documented yet but feel very strongly about.</p>
      <p>We offer a collaborative, high-growth environment where every employee is empowered to own their deliverables, leverage their bandwidth, and drive meaningful impact across the full spectrum of shirt-adjacent initiatives.</p>
      <p>We are an equal opportunity employer. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, gender, age, or preferred productivity methodology.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="riskr-careers__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-careers__jobs page-width">
    <div class="riskr-careers__jobs-header">
      <span class="riskr-careers__label">Open Roles</span>
      <span class="riskr-careers__jobs-count">6 positions</span>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-careers__job">
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-info">
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-title">Head of Synergy Facilitation</p>
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-meta">Full-time &middot; Remote &middot; Competitive Equity</p>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-desc">
        <p>Own the end-to-end synergy pipeline. Partner cross-functionally with our Alignment, Bandwidth, and Needle-Moving teams to ensure that all synergies are fully materialized before end of quarter. 5+ years of synergy experience required.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:careers@riskr.inc" class="riskr-careers__job-apply">Apply <span class="riskr-careers__arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-careers__job">
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-info">
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-title">Senior Cross-Functional Alignment Specialist</p>
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-meta">Full-time &middot; Hybrid &middot; Salary + Alignment Bonus</p>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-desc">
        <p>Drive alignment across all functions. Facilitate the kind of low-friction stakeholder engagement that moves the needle on cross-functional deliverables. Must be comfortable with ambiguity, matrices, and extended metaphors about journeys.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:careers@riskr.inc" class="riskr-careers__job-apply">Apply <span class="riskr-careers__arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-careers__job">
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-info">
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-title">VP of Bandwidth Optimization</p>
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-meta">Full-time &middot; On-site &middot; Executive Compensation</p>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-desc">
        <p>Lead our Bandwidth team in identifying, quantifying, and optimizing all available bandwidth across the organization. Define bandwidth KPIs. Present bandwidth dashboards to leadership weekly. Own the bandwidth roadmap.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:careers@riskr.inc" class="riskr-careers__job-apply">Apply <span class="riskr-careers__arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-careers__job">
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-info">
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-title">Director of Narrative Engineering</p>
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-meta">Full-time &middot; Remote &middot; Story-Based Compensation</p>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-desc">
        <p>Craft and maintain the Riskr story across all channels. Ensure our narrative is compelling, scalable, and defensible in a Series A context. Partner with PR to place stories in publications we have not yet confirmed will accept them.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:careers@riskr.inc" class="riskr-careers__job-apply">Apply <span class="riskr-careers__arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-careers__job">
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-info">
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-title">Cotton Sourcing &amp; Fiber Strategy Lead</p>
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-meta">Full-time &middot; Hybrid &middot; Competitive + Benefits</p>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-desc">
        <p>Own our end-to-end fiber supply chain. Develop and execute a multi-year cotton sourcing strategy that balances cost, quality, and ethical procurement. Must have opinions about thread counts. Pima cotton experience preferred.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:careers@riskr.inc" class="riskr-careers__job-apply">Apply <span class="riskr-careers__arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-careers__job">
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-info">
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-title">Founding Intern, Paradigm Disruption</p>
        <p class="riskr-careers__job-meta">Internship &middot; Remote &middot; Unpaid (Equity TBD)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-careers__job-desc">
        <p>Support senior leadership across all paradigm-disruption initiatives. Own special projects. Attend all-hands meetings and nod meaningfully. This is a rare opportunity to get in early on something that may or may not be a real company.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:careers@riskr.inc" class="riskr-careers__job-apply">Apply <span class="riskr-careers__arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="riskr-careers__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-careers__benefits page-width">
    <div class="riskr-careers__label-col">
      <span class="riskr-careers__label">Benefits</span>
    </div>
    <div class="riskr-careers__content-col">
      <ul class="riskr-careers__benefits-list">
        <li>Complimentary Riskr apparel (1 shirt per quarter, pending performance review)</li>
        <li>Unlimited PTO (subject to bandwidth availability)</li>
        <li>Remote-first culture (office TBD)</li>
        <li>Annual synergy offsite in a location to be determined by Q3</li>
        <li>Access to a shared Notion workspace with over 200 templates</li>
        <li>Competitive equity in a company with a valuation we are very confident about</li>
        <li>Weekly all-hands where leadership will be transparent about things they can be transparent about</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
  .riskr-careers {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .riskr-careers__hero {
    padding-block: 100px 80px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__subhead {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.52);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-careers__divider {
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-careers__culture {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 0 80px;
    padding-block: 72px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__label-col {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  .riskr-careers__content-col p {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__content-col p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .riskr-careers__jobs {
    padding-block: 64px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__jobs-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-careers__jobs-count {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  .riskr-careers__job {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr 120px;
    gap: 0 48px;
    align-items: start;
    padding-block: 28px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-careers__job-title {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .riskr-careers__job-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-careers__job-desc p {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-careers__job-apply {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    justify-self: end;
    white-space: nowrap;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .riskr-careers__job-apply:hover .riskr-careers__arrow {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  .riskr-careers__benefits {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 0 80px;
    padding-block: 72px;
  }

  .riskr-careers__benefits-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-careers__benefits-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    padding: 10px 0 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .riskr-careers__benefits-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .riskr-careers__culture,
    .riskr-careers__benefits {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      padding-block: 56px;
    }

    .riskr-careers__job {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    }

    .riskr-careers__job-apply {
      justify-self: start;
      grid-column: 1;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .riskr-careers__job-desc {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .riskr-careers__hero {
      padding-block: 72px 56px;
    }

    .riskr-careers__job {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .riskr-careers__job-apply {
      grid-column: 1;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Riskr Careers",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "riskr-careers-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Riskr Careers"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
